data.description: Discover the epitome of rural living in this charming 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom ranch home. Nestled amidst serene landscapes, this residence offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and rustic charm. Step into the spacious living areas flooded with natural light, accentuated by gleaming hardwood floors and a stone fireplace... The well-appointed kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and ample counter space for culinary enthusiasts. Retreat to the master suite with a luxurious en-suite bathroom featuring a spa-like soaking tub. A finished basement adds versatility to the living space, with a home office, guest bedroom and multiple entertainment area. The lower-level kitchen makes hosting summer pool parties ideal located close to the above ground pool. Host a large sports party utilizing the pristine wiffle ball field. This home embodies tranquility and convenience, providing a haven for those seeking a rural retreat with contemporary amenities. Experience the essence of country living in this idyllic ranch home.
